works.description: I have made maps called (dark threat & bloody wars) for a game called heroes of might and magic and I want to remove them, I have contacted by email "mailto:evgkuz@yandex.ru" to ask him to remove them but no response. There is no other function or help at the site like a login account so I can remove my own maps from the site. Everytime I write my name at Google search or any other search engine, this old site appears as results with links with my maps and my name on it which I'm enable to remove them. I also want to remove those links with my name as search results.
